OL,7,FA carer has been jailed for stealing
OL,8,Fmore than #125,000 from her patient to
OL,9,Fpay for a lavish holiday and to help
OL,10,Ffund her gambling addiction.
OL,12,FAnne Hill, 57, appeared at Nottingham
OL,13,FCrown Court on Monday 16 September and
OL,14,Fwas given the prison sentence after
OL,15,Fpreviously being found guilty of
OL,16,Fmultiple frauds.
