OL,7,FShe had been making online bank
OL,8,Ftransfers totalling #125,164.96 from
OL,9,Fher 86-year-old patient Louis Woodward
OL,10,Fbetween August 2019 and April 2021,
OL,11,Fthe trial heard.
OL,13,FShe also booked a 28-day holiday to
OL,14,FTurkey for her and her family costing
OL,15,Fover #7,000 ` although the Covid
OL,16,Fpandemic meant the trip was cancelled.
