OL,7,FShe was arrested after Mr Woodward's
OL,8,Ffriends raised suspicions about her,
OL,9,Fbut she denied any wrongdoing and said
OL,10,Fthat all funds she received were with
OL,11,Fhis consent.
OL,13,FShe also said she received funds to
OL,14,Fpay his bills and that he also gifted
OL,15,Fher #60,000 in September 2021.
