OL,7,FBut in Mr Woodward's video interview
OL,8,Fbefore he died, he said Hill only had
OL,9,Fpermission to use his money for his
OL,10,Fbenefit, such as payment of bills, and
OL,11,Fthat he did not gift her any money,
OL,12,Fbesides money to buy petrol.
OL,14,FThe court heard between May 2018 when
OL,15,Fshe was appointed power of attorney
OL,16,Fand April 2021 when she was arrested,
OL,17,FHill had net gambling losses of
OL,18,F#108,251.91 across more than 17,000
OL,19,Findividual transactions.
