OL,7,FDespite all the evidence, Hill, of
OL,8,FHawkins Close, Harworth, continued to
OL,9,Fdeny any wrongdoing and took the case
OL,10,Fto trial, where she was found guilty
OL,11,Fof five counts of fraud and one count
OL,12,Fof perverting the course of justice on
OL,13,FFriday 16 August.
OL,15,FIn his sentencing remarks, Judge Mark
OL,16,FWatson said: "This was a betrayal of
OL,17,Fthe very significant trust placed in
OL,18,Fyou. You deliberately targeted him
OL,19,Fbecause of his vulnerabilities.
