OL,7,F"You took what you wanted, when you
OL,8,Fwanted it, stripping him of his life
OL,9,Fsavings and then trying to take even
OL,10,Fmore."
OL,12,FAfter the sentencing, Detective
OL,13,FSergeant Daniel Weaver, who led the
OL,14,Finvestigation, said: "This was a very
OL,15,Fsad case in which a vulnerable,
OL,16,Felderly man was taken advantage of by
OL,17,Fsomeone he trusted.
