OL,7,F"It was only in the final months of Mr
OL,8,FWoodward's life that the full extent
OL,9,Fof Anne Hill's financial abuse was
OL,10,Fdiscovered, after a vigilant friend
OL,11,Fraised concerns.
OL,13,F"On being referred to Nottinghamshire
OL,14,FPolice, a swift arrest was made,
OL,15,Ffollowed by a detailed investigation
OL,16,Fwhich included working with various
OL,17,Fpartners to ensure Mr Woodward was
OL,18,Fthoroughly safeguarded in his final
OL,19,Fweeks and an in-depth review of
OL,20,Ffinancial data to build a strong case.
