OL,7,F"The other victims in this case are
OL,8,Fthe beneficiaries of Mr Woodward's
OL,9,Fwill ` the animal charities and long-
OL,10,Fstanding friends he had chosen to
OL,11,Fsupport after his death.
OL,13,F"We will now look to use the Proceeds
OL,14,Fof Crime Act to recover available
OL,15,Ffunds from Anne Hill, so that his
OL,16,Ffinal wishes can be fulfilled as far
OL,17,Fas possible.
