OL,7,F"Lasting Powers of Attorney exist to
OL,8,Fempower trusted persons to make
OL,9,Fimportant decisions in the best
OL,10,Finterests of another, often when they
OL,11,Fare at the most vulnerable stages of
OL,12,Ftheir lives. It is a powerful role
OL,13,Fthat comes with a lot of
OL,14,Fresponsibility, which most people take
OL,15,Fincredibly seriously and would never
OL,16,Fdream of abusing their authority.
