OL,7,F"However, I hope this case
OL,8,Fdemonstrates that where abuse does
OL,9,Ftake place, Nottinghamshire Police and
OL,10,Four partner agencies will work
OL,11,Ftogether to safeguard vulnerable
OL,12,Fpeople and ensure that perpetrators
OL,13,Fare held to account."
